'''John Fass Morton''' is an actor who played [[Dak Ralter]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']].<ref name="ESB" /> He also played [[Boba Fett]] in a scene when [[Jeremy Bulloch]] could not be present.<ref name="Insider 34">[[Star Wars Insider 34]]</ref>

